These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, 7up, milk
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, thai, malaysian, argentine
1. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
2. the argentine is on the left or right of the colombian##3
3. the colombian is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
5. the colombian is the person drinking cola##1
6. the person drinking 7up is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | milk  | juice | cola  | 7up |
| Nationality   | malaysian | argentine      | colombian | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, brazilian, polish, japanese
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, hedgehog, goldfish, turtle
1. the brazilian is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the turtle##2
2. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the japanese##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | japanese | polish | brazilian   | indian |
| Pet           | goldfish      | rabbit    | hedgehog | turtle      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, lemon, raspberry, blueberry
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, tram, scooter, boat
1. the person eating lemon is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
3. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
4. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
5. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
6. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | lemon | nectarine | raspberry     | blueberry |
| Transport   | tram  | boat   | scooter | ship    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, cooking, board-games, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, sports, comedy
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person watching sports movies##5
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
5. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | board-games | dancing | cooking | filmmaking |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | sports     | thriller    | action       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, apple, cherry, mango
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, time-travel, family, spy
1. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
2. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
3. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the left of the person eating carrot##5
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
6. the person eating mango is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | cherry | mango   | carrot   | apple    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | spy | romance | family |

