.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, manager, writer, dressmaker
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, spanish, australian, french
1. the dressmaker is in an odd position##4
2. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the french##5
3. the french is between the dressmaker and the australian##2
4. the writer is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Job           | fisherman | manager | dressmaker | writer |
| Nationality   | australian        | french     | chinese       | spanish   |

