.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, electronic, dubstep, folk
4 different pets are kept: pony, fish, bird, frog
1. the owner of the fish is the fan of folk##1
2. the fan of blues is between the fan of electronic and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the fan of blues##5
5. the fan of blues is in an even position##4
6. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | blues  | dubstep  | folk   |
| Pet           | frog  | pony | bird | fish |

