.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, lettuce, kale, onion
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, dressmaker, social-worker, firefighter
1. the dressmaker is on the right of the firefighter##1
2. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the social-worker##5
3. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
4. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person eating onion##1
5. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the entrepreneur##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food   | lettuce     | onion | kale     | peach   |
| Job    | firefighter | dressmaker  | social-worker | entrepreneur |

