.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, kiwi, watermelon, lettuce
1. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person eating lettuce##5
5. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
6. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the person eating watermelon##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | sprite | water   | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | cabbage       | watermelon   | lettuce | kiwi |

