.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, climbing, rowing, basketball
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
3. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
5. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | 7up | hot-chocolate       | milk   | sprite        |
| Sport      | climbing  | basketball | lacrosse | rowing |

