.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, reading, filmmaking, collecting
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, weightlifting, skateboarding, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | camping | reading   | filmmaking | collecting     |
| Sport   | weightlifting     | swimming | skateboarding  | tennis |

