2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
3. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5
4. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | comedy        | disaster        | musical |
| Sport         | water-polo  | weightlifting | rowing | swimming |

