.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, collecting, camping, fishing
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, security-guard, teacher, dancer
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
2. the accountant is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
5. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
6. the teacher is on the left of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | camping  | fishing      | collecting |
| Job     | teacher    | dancer | security-guard | accountant   |

