.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, iced-tea, 7up
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, reggae, house, pop
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the fan of pop##1
4. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
6. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking juice and the fan of reggae##2
7. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | juice   | iced-tea  | soy-milk      | 7up       |
| Music-Genre   | house | pop | reggae | ambient |

