3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the french is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | polish     | indian | french | indonesian |
| Transport     | van | ship    | bus    | boat |

