The people use 4 different means of transport: van, taxi, subway, car
1. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person driving the taxi and the owner of the cat##2
2. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
3. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet         | ferret   | fish   | hedgehog       | cat   |
| Transport   | subway | taxi | van | car |

