.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, peach, pineapple, tomato
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, airplane, quad-bike, jet-ski
1. the person eating peach is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
2. the person eating mango is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
5. the person eating peach is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
6. the person eating mango is between the person eating tomato and the person driving the trike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | peach     | tomato | mango | pineapple |
| Transport   | quad-bike | jet-ski | airplane      | trike        |

 